    <briefdescription>
<para><bold> Class <computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1fft__solver" kindref="compound">fft_solver</ref></computeroutput> contains the FFTW3 data structures for Fourier transformation of Green&apos;s functions. </bold> </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Purpose</title><para></para>
</simplesect>
<blockquote><para>This class contains FFT as member functions to transform Green&apos;s function objects. </para>
</blockquote></para>
<para>Given:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1fft__solver_a8be74d857b3fcddba40d07c689de30b4_1a8be74d857b3fcddba40d07c689de30b4" kindref="member">nt_</ref></computeroutput>: Number of time points (of the <computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1GF" kindref="compound">GF</ref></computeroutput> object).</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1fft__solver_a117ae181557a9e9697b71a24c625bd99_1a117ae181557a9e9697b71a24c625bd99" kindref="member">nfreq_</ref></computeroutput>: Number of frequency points. The frequency <computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1GF" kindref="compound">GF</ref></computeroutput> needs <formula id="270">$ {\tt nfreq} = 2/3 ({\tt nt} - 1) $</formula> frequency points for the FFT to work.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1fft__solver_a53a228901f43541a1092096b33aa7428_1a53a228901f43541a1092096b33aa7428" kindref="member">Nft_</ref></computeroutput>: Total number of FFT points, <formula id="271">$ {\tt Nft\_} = 2 ({\tt nt\_}-1)$</formula>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1fft__solver_a1f28a071909e468cfce7c69e9b04fa4f_1a1f28a071909e468cfce7c69e9b04fa4f" kindref="member">in</ref></computeroutput>: Internal FFT input array, <ref refid="classness_1_1GF" kindref="compound">GF</ref> data are read in. Has length <computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1fft__solver_a53a228901f43541a1092096b33aa7428_1a53a228901f43541a1092096b33aa7428" kindref="member">Nft_</ref></computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1fft__solver_a059843fb475da87510c99b10e555f0ed_1a059843fb475da87510c99b10e555f0ed" kindref="member">out</ref></computeroutput>: Internal FFT output array, data are read out of this array.. Has length <computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1fft__solver_a53a228901f43541a1092096b33aa7428_1a53a228901f43541a1092096b33aa7428" kindref="member">Nft_</ref></computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1fft__solver_a8914b55e18bb144036778ee81842c890_1a8914b55e18bb144036778ee81842c890" kindref="member">plan_for</ref></computeroutput>: FFTW plan for forward transform (here to time)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput><ref refid="classness_1_1fft__solver_a8b9856823b939e73a3a087d37f7f6696_1a8b9856823b939e73a3a087d37f7f6696" kindref="member">plan_back</ref></computeroutput>: FFTW plan for backward transform (here to frequency) </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
